{"tid":2211433,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"沙中綫醜聞吹哨者 中科興業今被頒令清盤","createTime":"2020-09-21T06:33:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T06:38:50.000Z","uid":339805,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ae56eced2a58ca05dda7c5c5db438e9f1e936afa","tid":2211433,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T06:33:58.000Z","msg":"沙中綫紅磡站工程分判商中科興業董事總經理潘焯鴻，揭發工程出現剪鋼筋等多項醜聞。中科興業及後遭入稟追數兼被法庭判敗訴，卻未有還款，去年遭債權人入稟高等法院呈請清盤。案件今早再度開庭，法官在中科興業未能作出任何承諾下，頒下清盤令。<br />\n<br />\n債權人Siu Kai Construction早前入稟區域法院，向中科興業追討約共300萬元，法院去年8月在中科興業未有抗辯下，直接判債權人勝訴。中科興業其後申請擱置判令，但遭駁回；中科興業本已就此提出上訴，案件原排期至11月處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200921/237KILHXEJE2PPL3YSUMF32DCE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0ST2vEFTIC3mpFX8V2nVZuSZk74crkyaZRSu7moo4iKKzHc65LfwJzvj4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200921%2F237KILHXEJE2PPL3YSUMF32DCE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0ST2vEFTIC3mpFX8V2nVZuSZk74crkyaZRSu7moo4iKKzHc65LfwJzvj4&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZop1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=2600aa6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200921%2F237KILHXEJE2PPL3YSUMF32DCE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0ST2vEFTIC3mpFX8V2nVZuSZk74crkyaZRSu7moo4iKKzHc65LfwJzvj4&h=c6e1999d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200921/237KILHXEJE2PPL3YSUMF32DCE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0ST2vEFTIC3mpFX8V2nVZuSZk74crkyaZRSu7moo4iKKzHc65LfwJzvj4</a>"},{"pid":"5839738fd28d1fcdbd235064d2ba2a3efc83a601","tid":2211433,"uid":215734,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl